* Iron Raptor clenched her eyes shit as the pain went up a notch, making her 
breaths come hard and ragged.
What was wrong with her!!
There was no damage, her scans proved that.
But then what was wrong?!
A wave of nausia passed through her as the pain suddenly increased...but 
then died away just as quickly as it came...leaving behind the feeling as if 
she were about to throw up.
Iron Raptor leaned back against the wall, her breathing deep, opening up her 
eyes.
She turned her head to Prowl, a very tired expression on her face.*

" I don't know. It's just a pain that comes and goes...and I don't know 
why."

* Her voice was winded, she then looking down at her mech-fluid covered 
body.
She eased herself off the wall and stood up, her motions still expresively 
tired.*

" I have to get myself cleaned off."

* She looked up at Prowl.*

" Maybe it's time you showed me your quarters, and your shower."
